column5: Hello - Looking for a Cabin or House to rent for a week in September 2009 on Rainy Lake. It can be on the US or Canadian side, but would prefer the US side. THis is for a group of 6 guys. We'd also be open to a resort with a stand-alone house or cabin for rent. I'm confident you folks will know of some places - thanks in advance for your help! Scott
Island view resort has cabins and a bar and restaurant....on the US side. 15 miles east of International Falls
